    "body": "I do believe this changed recently, but I believe that it was that it no longer accepts `null` to do a random port, and now requires `0` for node 8.  But I did not look up docs on this, so I could be wrong.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Ok, just tried it with node 8 and 6.  In node 6 `null` and `0` work, `undefined` fails.  In node 8, `null` fails and `0` and `undefined` work.",
